reviewText:
Of all the Australia dvds I could have selected, I picked this one because I expected a detailed tour of the Sydney Opera house - it's right there ON THE COVER.

Spends about 5 minutes there.
I really enjoyed this as I am thinking of taking a trip there and it gives me some ideas as to what I want to see.

Australia is such a stunning country, we loved this video. The only reason I am not giving it five stars is because it was sadly lacking information on Australia's wonderful wine country, vineyards, etc.
